{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communications", "channel": "media_relations", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Hey team, let's schedule a meeting to discuss the upcoming press release for our new store opening in Vancouver. Any suggestions for the best time?", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communications", "channel": "media_relations", "user": "mark_kim", "message": "Hi Andrew, I suggest having the meeting tomorrow at 10 AM. I'll prepare the initial draft by then.", "created_at": 1620500600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "sustainability_research", "user": "jane_lee", "message": "I've just received the results from our latest energy efficiency audit. It looks like our efforts in reducing energy consumption at our stores are paying off!", "created_at": 1620501200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "corporate_communications", "channel": "media_relations", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Thanks for your suggestion, Mark. Let's set the meeting for 10 AM tomorrow. Please share the draft in advance so we can review it.", "created_at": 1620501800000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "sustainability_research", "user": "jane_lee", "message": "I'll be sharing the detailed report of the energy audit with all of you soon. Let's analyze it together and plan our next steps accordingly.", "created_at": 1620502400000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "sustainability_research", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "In our efforts to continue strengthening our sustainability initiatives, we've started a new research project. This year, we decided to focus on customer perception and attitude towards our transparency in revealing our carbon footprint, specifically in our delivery operations.", "create_at": 1610064000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "sustainability_research", "user": "jane_lee", "message": "That's great, Andrew. I think it's an important step to understand our customers' attitudes towards environmental transparency. Are we also looking at how this transparency might influence their shopping behaviors?", "create_at": 1610067600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sustainability_initiatives", "channel": "sustainability_research", "user": "andrew.park", "message": "Indeed, Jane. Part of the research is to measure how the disclosure of our delivery carbon footprints might influence shopping behaviors. We believe that being open about these impacts will not only positively affect customer perception but also give us a competitive edge in the market.", "create_at": 1610071200000}}
